<title>量化群已满，欢迎加新群</title>
<link>https://henix.github.io/feeds/zhuanlan.c_106548378/2018-09-19-44945051.html</link>
<description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/44945051&quot;&gt;原文&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;各个群还是讨论量化为主，&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-1fe650f06e3e82cde2bf55cfa20c779c_r.jpg&quot; data-caption=&quot;&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;272&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;545&quot; data-watermark=&quot;watermark&quot; data-original-src=&quot;v2-1fe650f06e3e82cde2bf55cfa20c779c&quot; data-watermark-src=&quot;v2-14cdab118336b28550a135f73bd75445&quot; data-private-watermark-src=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;有偏学术一点的&lt;/p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-b784d0d6b22ac4e5b9df6bf26860af30_r.jpg&quot; data-caption=&quot;&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;252&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;527&quot; data-watermark=&quot;watermark&quot; data-original-src=&quot;v2-b784d0d6b22ac4e5b9df6bf26860af30&quot; data-watermark-src=&quot;v2-f7d1ead3fe4e4fed4433499b0ffbcd52&quot; data-private-watermark-src=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;有炒币的&lt;/p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-e291a4e600534840fe1376f3cad357e8_r.jpg&quot; data-caption=&quot;&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;272&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;535&quot; data-watermark=&quot;watermark&quot; data-original-src=&quot;v2-e291a4e600534840fe1376f3cad357e8&quot; data-watermark-src=&quot;v2-8929daa4e30d1ed8d697fae0a05ac1d3&quot; data-private-watermark-src=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;有讨论图像识别来做的&lt;/p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-932b250ccc9c6004cda6833fc5db7978_r.jpg&quot; data-caption=&quot;&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;278&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;569&quot; data-watermark=&quot;watermark&quot; data-original-src=&quot;v2-932b250ccc9c6004cda6833fc5db7978&quot; data-watermark-src=&quot;v2-c46f739f53f39d66120f4ab4ddf604e7&quot; data-private-watermark-src=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;有讨论数学背景做量化的&lt;/p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-a1d74e23a0ad1a9f41ef73e74c449c72_r.jpg&quot; data-caption=&quot;&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;262&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;527&quot; data-watermark=&quot;watermark&quot; data-original-src=&quot;v2-a1d74e23a0ad1a9f41ef73e74c449c72&quot; data-watermark-src=&quot;v2-ee1ade2f9820251967d41f0ae98a18a2&quot; data-private-watermark-src=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;做量化也有美女&lt;/p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-002922a7ecd39d5e9016a37b2b7239a7_r.jpg&quot; data-caption=&quot;&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;271&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;541&quot; data-watermark=&quot;watermark&quot; data-original-src=&quot;v2-002922a7ecd39d5e9016a37b2b7239a7&quot; data-watermark-src=&quot;v2-b0dff0d30069dc97d2150b8aa39e86a5&quot; data-private-watermark-src=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;只是最近金融圈风花雪月之事较多，偶尔歪群在所难免，但除非群友强烈谴责，我一般不会踢人。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;目前这些群基本都满了，但我会建新群。目前微信似乎3天不通过就过期了，所以我一般会尽快通过，但要积累到一定人数之后才建群，中间要等一定时间，请原来那个。大家有兴趣的话可以加我微信aaliwei91，注明“知乎量化加群”，谢谢。&lt;/p&gt;</description>
